{
  "stem": "1419.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was-- it was nothing there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was just a big hanger, hanger.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We all had to sleep on the floor.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we had to build a little  kitchen on the site.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We were-- we were not getting any food for a while, just bread.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then after they built a kitchen, we had-- we had to go to work.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Five some.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We were not too many over there, maybe 60 people or so, not too many.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And then coming from work, we used to get every five men, staying in, in the particular row, used to get a washbasin.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And they walked up to the-- to the-- to the kitchen.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And the wash-- they, they give you soup at the washbasin.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And everybody had a spoon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And everybody had to eat from the washbasin.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "You had to be lucky to be with somebody couldn't eat fast enough or he knows you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "If not, you would be left with just water on top.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "That's how they'd feed us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There were no more chimneys when we arrived in Birkenau.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We didn't-- we didn't-- we, we didn't know about it.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't see it anyway.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't see it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe there were, but I didn't see any chimneys.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We, we didn't see anything.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were only over there two days, I think.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, in the last camp, in Ganacker, in, in April, 19-- in 1945, we came to-- we came-- we, we're working, like I told you, at the airfield.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they make a big Appelplatz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "On the Appelplatz, you know, they called all the prisoners out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they, they told us to get ready.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We're going to march out.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
